page.title: 11Felixstowes G.E.Square
page.content: {The Great Eastern Square }has only just been completed and it is greatly improved compared with the old tumble down railway station and car park.It has now been converted into a{shopping {arcade}with shops such as a bakery, Solar,Lighters and a carpet shop. Behind the arcade is a big car park and behind this is the new station. On the square in front of the shops there is a market on one of the old station platforms. All of the old station buildings have been repainted and done up and new Solar building which has been put on the side and it fits on very well to the old buildings. On the side of Solar they have built a new chemist. The shops inside Solar range from food shops to stationary shops like{Spats.
